body:
Caught in the middle of a dangerous place where I wasn&#039;t supposed to be, as one of the squishiest most immobile champs in the game, surrounded by champions that are known for not letting their prey go _(and I was a very high priority target too)_.

{{champion:45}} 

I was pulled **from the fire** by a god of a man!

{{champion:412}} 

I am almost mad that I lived, just because it _genuinely_ should have been impossible!

Im not sure if TEND frequents the boards, and if he does and sees this, I thank you sir!
I wish there were medals that could be earned in league, because this man deserves the highest honour.


{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
